ー"]}, {"box": [462, 959, 503, 1013], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22, "lines_coords": [[[481.0, 959.0], [503.0, 959.0], [503.0, 1013.0], [481.0, 1013.0]], [[462.0, 959.0], [484.0, 959.0], [484.0, 1013.0], [462.0, 1013.0]]], "lines": ["イタタ", "タタ．．．"]}], "img_path": "031.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.7", "img_width": 838, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [670, 78, 716, 177], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22, "lines_coords": [[[695.0, 78.0], [716.0, 78.0], [716.0, 150.0], [695.0, 150.0]], [[670.0, 78.0], [692.0, 78.0], [693.0, 146.0], [671.0, 146.0]]], "lines": ["痛いよー", "痛いよー"]}, {"box": [491, 77, 607, 180], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18, "lines_coords": [[[586.0, 79.0], [605.0, 79.0], [605.0, 175.0], [586.0, 175.0]], [[563.0, 78.0], [583.0, 78.0], [583.0, 179.0], [563.0, 179.0]], [[537.0, 77.0], [557.0, 77.0], [560.0, 174.0], [540.0, 174.0]], [[518.0, 78.0], [534.0, 78.0], [534.0, 154.0], [518.0, 154.0]], [[493.0, 78.0], [511.0, 78.0], [508.0, 174.0], [491.0, 174.0]]], "lines": ["いたたた．．．", "困ったわね、", "この嵐じゃ", "病院にも", "行けない．．"]}, {"box": [239, 76, 322, 193], "vertical": true, "font_size": 27, "lines_coords": [[[297.0, 77.0], [322.0, 77.0], [322.0, 169.0], [297.0, 169.0]], [[269.0, 76.0], [294.0, 76.0], [294.0, 193.0], [269.0, 193.0]], [[239.0, 76.0], [270.0, 76.0], [270.0, 131.0], [239.0, 131.0]]], "lines": ["私の足の", "うおの目が", "．．．？"]}, {"box": [345, 308, 458, 401], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25, "lines_coords": [[[430.0, 309.0], [454.0, 308.0], [458.0, 400.0], [433.0, 401.0]], [[402.0, 308.0], [431.0, 308.0], [431.0, 382.0], [402.0, 382.0]], [[377.0, 309.0], [398.0, 309.0], [398.0, 401.0], [377.0, 401.0]], [[345.0, 308.0], [370.0, 308.0], [370.0, 379.0], [345.0, 379.0]]], "lines": ["ああっ．．．", "これは", "どうした", "事だ！？"]}, {"box": [451, 708, 512, 789], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23, "lines_coords": [[[491.0, 711.0], [512.0, 711.0], [512.0, 788.0], [491.0, 788.0]], [[466.0, 708.0], [491.0, 708.0], [491.0, 769.0], [466.0, 769.0]]], "lines": ["お父さん", "これは"]}, {"box"