0, 103.0], [741.0, 103.0], [741.0, 201.0], [721.0, 201.0]]], "lines": ["．．．．．．何だ", "．．．そうか．．．"]}, {"box": [469, 99, 512, 298], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18, "lines_coords": [[[492.0, 99.0], [512.0, 99.0], [512.0, 291.0], [492.0, 291.0]], [[471.0, 101.0], [487.0, 101.0], [487.0, 297.0], [471.0, 297.0]]], "lines": ["とにかく：これからも", "力を合わせていこうな。"]}, {"box": [358, 86, 425, 208], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19, "lines_coords": [[[407.0, 87.0], [424.0, 87.0], [424.0, 205.0], [407.0, 205.0]], [[382.0, 86.0], [402.0, 86.0], [402.0, 201.0], [382.0, 201.0]], [[358.0, 86.0], [378.0, 86.0], [378.0, 152.0], [358.0, 152.0]]], "lines": ["君は疲れてる。", "坊やをかして", "ごらん。"]}, {"box": [119, 84, 191, 164], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26, "lines_coords": [[[165.0, 84.0], [191.0, 84.0], [191.0, 144.0], [165.0, 144.0]], [[141.0, 85.0], [167.0, 85.0], [167.0, 164.0], [141.0, 164.0]], [[119.0, 85.0], [144.0, 85.0], [144.0, 154.0], [119.0, 154.0]]], "lines": ["俺達が", "おぶって", "いくよ。"]}, {"box": [691, 404, 766, 472], "vertical": true, "font_size": 29, "lines_coords": [[[739.0, 407.0], [766.0, 407.0], [766.0, 457.0], [739.0, 457.0]], [[714.0, 406.0], [745.0, 406.0], [745.0, 472.0], [714.0, 472.0]], [[691.0, 404.0], [721.0, 404.0], [721.0, 460.0], [691.0, 460.0]]], "lines": ["いえ、", "大丈夫", "です。"]}, {"box": [567, 403, 616, 467], "vertical": true, "font_size": 28, "lines_coords": [[[590.0, 405.0], [616.0, 405.0], [616.0, 466.0], [590.0, 466.0]], [[567.0, 403.0], [597.0, 403.0], [597.0, 467.0], [567.0, 467.0]]], "lines": ["大丈夫", "って．．．"]}, {"box": [382, 399, 474, 506], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23, "lines_coords": [[[453.0, 403.0], [474.0, 403.0], [474.0, 479.0], [453.0, 479.0]], [[424.0, 399.0], [454.0, 399.0], [454.0, 437.0], [424.0, 437.0]], [[405.0, 403.0], [425.0, 403.0], [425.0, 505.0], [405.0, 505.0]], [[382.0, 400.0], [403.0, 400.0], [403.0, 464.0], [382.0, 464.0]]], "lines": ["これから", "先、", "長いんだぜ。", "さあ！"]}, {"box": [723, 679, 771, 746], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26, "lines_coords